flowchart LR
 A[Admin / Receptionist] --> S[Admission Servlets]
 V[Doctor / Nurse / Patient / Billing read-only] --> S
 S --> AS[AdmissionService]
 AS --> AD[AdmissionDao]
 AS --> BD[BedDao]
 AS --> RD[RoomDao]
 AS --> Bill[BillDao]
 AD --> O[(Oracle XE)]
 BD --> O
 RD --> O
 AS --> L{Lock admission and beds}
 L -->|unavailable or duplicate| Block[Block operation]
 L --> Admit[Admit + occupy]
 L --> Transfer[Release + occupy + transfer history]
 L --> Discharge[Discharge + release + room charge]
